# Opponent Bots
Quincy â†’ Cycles through [R, P, S, R, P].
Abbey â†’ Predicts based on your 2nd-last move.
Kris â†’ Random but skewed distribution.
Mrugesh â†’ Plays your most common move in the last 10 rounds.

# AI Strategy (Your Bot)
Starts with fixed moves to gather data.
Detects if the opponent is â€œKrisâ€ (counters your last move).
Uses Markov chain prediction to model opponent patterns.
Falls back to a cycle strategy if no data is available.

